{
  "stem": "3165.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And some of the Gestapos were with them, and the others took them into the torture room.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And he was a 14-year-old.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they tortured him the same way.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And again, my father said, 'I heard him scream just terrible.' And then they threw him out again to the room.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And then they took my father in to the torture room and they did the same thing to him, beating him and torturing him.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And then my father said, then-- then they threw him out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And my father was-- I guess they took my brothers away, and my father was too sick to get up.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And all I heard him say that he-- he was-- he was dying, so they sent him back to die at home.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And then he says to my mother, call all the girls here fast.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I want to make a blessing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I don't know where my two older sisters were, but my youngest sister, Susan, she brought in Susan.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I was in the room already.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So I got up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I heard him say.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And my mother brought in my younger sister.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And my father put his hand on my head and gave me a blessing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And then he put his hand on my youngest sister, and he blessed her.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And he just closed his eyes and died.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] And of course, I never say my brothers again.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] That's what [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] this war was doing to us Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After that, again, I-- I-- my mother was a strong woman.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never heard her scream or yell, or-- she was just saying, praying, and just said, we've got to keep you girls.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We've got to do something now.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
